DESCRIPTION:Confronting anguish through humor\, Sad Boys in Harpy Land is
  a semi-autobiographical clown show about self-doubt and the artist’s 
 journey. Through a series of existential vignettes\, self-proclaimed “
 experimental clown artist” Alex Tatarsky fuses together fragments of t
 heir own story...\nMore info: https://thevisualist.org/2026/01/alex-tata
 rsky-sad-boys-in-harpy-land/\nVenue site: https://visit.mcachicago.org/e
 vents/alex-tatarsky-sad-boys-in-harpy-land/
